title: CFTC to Review Prediction Market Kalshi’s Contracts to Bet on Control of Congress
description: The Commodity Futures Trading Commission will decide on June 26 whether to start a formal 90-day review of prediction market provider KalshiEX’s contract that allows users to bet on which party takes control of the U.S. Congress.
